          <updateDate>2018-04-17T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><a name="summary">This bill allow</a>s administrative or judicial review of additional Medicare disproportionate share hospital (DSH) payment determinations for&nbsp;acute care hospitals known as subsection (d) hospitals. Under current law, the Centers for Medicare &amp; Medicaid Services&nbsp;must make DSH payments&nbsp;to&nbsp;qualifying hospitals that treat a disproportionate share of low-income patients.</p>]]></text>
        </item>
